 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">            <div class=\\\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--features panel entry-content wc-tab\\\" id=\\\"tab-features\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"tab-title-features\\\">\\t\\t\\t\\t                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-list\\\">                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-name\\\">Easy Clean Enamel Oven Interior</div>                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-desc\\\">The grease does not stick to the surface and can therefore be cleaned more easily.</div>                                                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-image\\\"><img src=\\\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marketplace-midmanphilippines/us.ilve.com/refs/heads/main/static/features/1380.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Easy Clean Enamel Oven Interior\\\"></div>                        </div>                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-list\\\">                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-name\\\">Total Black Brass Burner With Non-Stick Nanotechnological Coating</div>                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-desc\\\">The noble technical characteristics of brass are enriched with a nanotechnological coating that assures easy cleaning, with an elegant Total Black finish.</div>                                                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-image\\\"><img src=\\\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marketplace-midmanphilippines/us.ilve.com/refs/heads/main/static/features/1447.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Total Black Brass Burner With Non-Stick Nanotechnological Coating\\\"></div>                        </div>                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-list\\\">                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-name\\\">Cooktop (Hob) With Cast Iron Pan Supports</div>                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-desc\\\">The indestructible cast iron pan supports provide a functional and safe support for the pots.</div>                                                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-image\\\"><img src=\\\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marketplace-midmanphilippines/us.ilve.com/refs/heads/main/static/features/1448.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Cooktop (Hob) With Cast Iron Pan Supports\\\"></div>                        </div>                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-list\\\">                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-name\\\">Highly Specialized Cooktops</div>                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-desc\\\">Built with AISI 304 steel and 12/10 thickness, choose your ideal combination between gas burner cooktop or induction, mixed configuration and in various setups.</div>                                                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-image\\\"><img src=\\\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marketplace-midmanphilippines/us.ilve.com/refs/heads/main/static/features/1449.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Highly Specialized Cooktops\\\"></div>                        </div>                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-list\\\">                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-name\\\">Dual Gas Burners With Power Up To 20000 BTU As Standard</div>                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-desc\\\">Optimal supply and perfect distribution of the heat, for all types of cooking.</div>                                                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-image\\\"><img src=\\\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marketplace-midmanphilippines/us.ilve.com/refs/heads/main/static/features/1474.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Dual Gas Burners With Power Up To 20000 BTU As Standard\\\"></div>                        </div>                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-list\\\">                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-name\\\">4.3 Inch Full Touch Display</div>                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-desc\\\">Thanks to TFT technology, the display assures superior readability, displaying every function with clear and immediate graphics. Simply touch the large display with one finger to control all the functions of the single oven or of the two ovens, with a single device. Temperature, timer, and automatic cooking start and end programmer: everything is controlled with one move and at a glance.</div>                                                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-image\\\"><img src=\\\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marketplace-midmanphilippines/us.ilve.com/refs/heads/main/static/features/1475.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"4.3 Inch Full Touch Display\\\"></div>                        </div>                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-list\\\">                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-name\\\">Ilve\\u2019S Majestic Statement</div>                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-desc\\\">A fusion of beauty and functionality that combines the classic Italian style and cutting-edge technology. Majestic is a bold, masterful embodiment of the ultimate range cooker that will decorate your home with their rounded shapes forged in pure steel with painstakingly made details.</div>                                                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-image\\\"><img src=\\\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marketplace-midmanphilippines/us.ilve.com/refs/heads/main/static/features/1496.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Ilve\\u2019S Majestic Statement\\\"></div>                        </div>                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-list\\\">                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-name\\\">The Statement Range Cooker Which Makes Your Kitchen Unique</div>                            <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-desc\\\">Aesthetics is important, but that\\u2019s not all. It is essential to have the best technologies available to cook well and with pleasure. ILVE puts all its experience and research at your service, offering solutions that combine top-level performance and maximum simplicity, safety and user-friendliness: to always guarantee the best satisfaction.</div>                                                        <div class=\\\"pro-2024-feature-image\\\"><img src=\\\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marketplace-midmanphilippines/us.ilve.com/refs/heads/main/static/features/1497.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"The Statement Range Cooker Which Makes Your Kitchen Unique\\\"></div>                        </div>\\t\\t\\t</div>         </div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_specification\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_specification\\\" data-slug=\\\"specification\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Specification</span> </span></h3>      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_specification\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_specification\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">               <table class=\\\"woocommerce-product-attributes shop_attributes\\\" aria-label=\\\"Product Details\\\">\\t\\t\\t<tr class=\\\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--pa_of67_brand\\\">\\t\\t\\t<th class=\\\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\\\" scope=\\\"row\\\">Brand</th>\\t\\t\\t<td class=\\\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\\\">ILVE</td>\\t\\t</tr>\\t\\t\\t<tr class=\\\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--pa_o338_series\\\">\\t\\t\\t<th class=\\\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\\\" scope=\\\"row\\\">Series</th>\\t\\t\\t<td class=\\\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\\\">Majestic II</td>\\t\\t</tr>\\t\\t\\t<tr class=\\\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--pa_o53b_appliancecategory\\\">\\t\\t\\t<th clas